# A citizen of the country [[Afghanistan]]. The word 'Afghanistani' refers to someone who possesses the nationality of [[Afghanistan]], no matter of what race or background. This word has been used recently by those citizens of [[Afghanistan]] who are not [[Pashtun]] because the word [[Afghan]] mainly reflects [[Pashtun]] citizens. 

